<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3669.1.8>
    dc:creator "Maruyama, Munetoshi; Kamezawa, Hiromu" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Adinopsis nippon, a new species of marsh-dwelling rove beetle (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae: Deinopsini) from Japan, with an annotated catalogue of Adinopsis species of the world" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223135>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223136> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223135>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 8. Adinopsis nippon Maruyama & Kamezawa, sp. n.: 2, left mandible; 3, right galea; 4, apical half of male tergite VIII; 5, male abdominal tergite IX (half), and X; 6, median lobe of aedeagus (holotype); 7, apical lobe of paramere (holotype); 8, spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/223135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223136>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Habitats of Adinopsis nippon Maruyama & Kamezawa, sp. n. and Deinopsis modesta Sharp in riverbed of Edo-gawa (Shôwa-machi). 9, 10, Distant views of the riverbed, with predominant Phragmites australis grasses; 11, 12, Carex communities between Phragmites australis grasses and Salix trees." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/223136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

